                    "text": "<b>Requirements</b> The giant mosquito has a creature grabbed; <b>Effect</b> The giant mosquito uses its proboscis to drain blood from the grabbed creature. This deals 3d6 damage, and the giant mosquito gains temporary Hit Points equal to the damage dealt. A creature that has its blood drained by a giant mosquito is <a aonid=\"10\" game-obj=\"Conditions\">drained 1</a> until it receives healing of any kind or amount.",
